¡Alto!

41
00:06:13,630 --> 00:06:16,800
Mola

42
00:06:13,630 --> 00:06:16,800
Shi

43
00:06:13,630 --> 00:06:16,800
Chibukai

44
00:06:13,630 --> 00:06:16,800
Fansub!

45
00:06:13,630 --> 00:06:16,800
Tama viene de "tamago" (huevo).

46
